{"tid":813504,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該有病就唔好返工啦","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:41:25.000Z","uid":150912,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f74cb9d503068c1d7bc8ce17c7b8e56c77a8a39","tid":813504,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"上個星期有條友病<br />\n仲要夾硬返工<br />\n已經搞到同部門3個人都病左<br />\nD野堆到山咁做唔切都算<br />\n之後到星期5終於惹到我都有D作病<br />\n原本休息2日已經好好多 <br />\n點知今日一返到去即刻加劇<br />\n已經3年冇病過,強壯如牛的我依家終於發埋燒<br />\n唔該你班大帝有病就唔好返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司依家簡直變左變種劇毒溫床<br />\n個個係到交叉感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babddf675c638ff81f4e376841049db2df9bdfba","tid":813504,"uid":55080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:21:24.000Z","msg":"On9....請到先得架<br />\n請到又要睇人面色"},{"pid":"0e7704bfff57a195426b1dd0b250e4cf44fce542","tid":813504,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"babddf675c638ff81f4e376841049db2df9bdfba","tid":813504,"uid":55080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:21:24.000Z","msg":"On9....請到先得架<br />\n請到又要睇人面色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"點解請唔到<br />\n最後果條帶菌者今朝想返工<br />\n坐左1個鐘後俾老細叫佢返屋企<br />\n佢今日如果唔出現<br />\n我都唔會病"},{"pid":"2d4aa57bfe10f5fcaeab29735fb968ba8a215651","tid":813504,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"唉好撚辛苦<br />\n成個身慶恰恰<br />\n但又好怕凍,一凍就痛<br />\n狂流鼻水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐冇感受到發燒係咩感覺<br />\n可唔可以快D退燒<br />\n我聽日仲係好想返工呀"},{"pid":"4e462d5f3f5ed7c8186132a17997bf0d9f9fafa6","tid":813504,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4aa57bfe10f5fcaeab29735fb968ba8a215651","tid":813504,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"唉好撚辛苦<br />\n成個身慶恰恰<br />